## Common Tasks

### Adding a New Page
1. Create `src/app/[route]/page.tsx`
2. Use `ModuleLayout` or appropriate layout component
3. Follow existing page patterns
4. Add to `HeaderNav` if needed
5. Test in both themes

### Adding a New Component
1. Create in `src/components/`
2. Use semantic tokens (no inline styles)
3. Support dark/light themes
4. Add TypeScript types
5. Export from component file

### Updating Brand Tokens
1. Update `brand-guidelines/brand-tokens.css`
2. Update `src/app/globals.css` semantic tokens
3. Test across all pages
4. Verify contrast ratios
5. Document changes

